    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_04-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "1、2、3、4……\nここで……決める！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "1‚ 2‚ 3‚ 4…\nI’ll… decide it here!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_suzvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "suzvillastudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_04-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ、はぁ……\nこれくらいで終わりにしようか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huff‚ huff‚ huff…\nLet’s stop here for today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_suzvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "suzvillastudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_04-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "は～！　お疲れ様～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ha! Good work!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_04-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "最後の最後まで集中しましたわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You were focused until the very end.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_suzvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "suzvillastudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_04-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、凄くいい感じに踊れたんじゃないかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone‚ I think we were able to dance really well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_suzvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "suzvillastudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_04-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "合宿期間中に、また一段とレベルアップ出来ましたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We were able to level up even more during the training camp.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_suzvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "suzvillastudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_04-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "そうね。すずに提案された時は驚いたけど……\n合宿に来て本当に良かったと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. I was surprised when Suzu suggested it…\nbut I’m really glad we came to this training camp.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.3126466035,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_04-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、この後は――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then‚ after this――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_suzvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "suzvillastudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_04-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、探検の続きだよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ we’re continuing our exploration!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_suzvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "suzvillastudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_04-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "今晩が最後のチャンス……絶対に見つけますわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tonight’s our last chance… We’ll definitely find it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_suzvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "suzvillastudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_04-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "……ふふ\nはいはい、分かったから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Fufu.\nOkay‚ okay‚ I get it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_villaroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "villaroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 57.1
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_villaroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "villaroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 57.1
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_outside-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 57.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_04-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "今日はどの辺りを探そっか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Where should we search today?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_04-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "それなら今日はこちらを……\n開けた場所はあらかた探しましたわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then let's go this way…\nWe've already searched most of the open areas.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_villaroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "villaroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 66.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_04-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣もすずも、よく諦めずに探し続けられるわね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei and Suzu‚ you never give up searching…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_04-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣ちゃんとすずちゃんだけじゃないみたいだよ、ほら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems like it’s not just Mei-chan and Suzu-chan‚ look.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_villaroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "villaroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 75.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_04-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "「オカピの移動速度はとてもゆっくりで\nメスはオスより行動範囲が広い」……なるほど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Okapis move very slowly‚\nand females have a wider range of activity than males.”… I see.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_villaroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "villaroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 85.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_04-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "食べる植物の種類はかなり多いようなので\n植物分布で居場所を推測するのは難しそうです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They seem to eat a wide variety of plants‚ so\nit seems difficult to estimate their location based on plant distribution.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_04-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "探しているオカピはメスですから\n行動範囲や移動速度を考えると……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since the okapi we’re looking for is female‚\nconsidering her range of activity and movement speed…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.3000000101,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_villaroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "villaroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 98.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_04-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "沙季まであんなに熱心になるなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even Saki is so enthusiastic…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_villaroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "villaroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 101.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_04-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "沙季ちゃんの好奇心に火がついたみたいだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It looks like Saki-chan's curiosity has been ignited.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_04-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "でも、なんだかんだで探検してる時も結構動くでしょ？\nいい基礎トレーニングになってるんじゃないかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ we move around quite a bit during our explorations anyway‚ right?\nI think it’s become good basic training.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_villaroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "villaroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 112.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_04-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "確かに……\n毎晩トレイルランニングをしてるようなものだしね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Indeed…\nIt’s like we’re trail running every night.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_moon-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 118.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_villaroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "villaroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 118.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_villaroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "villaroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 121.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_04-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "こういうのも悪くないかな\nみんなではしゃぐこの感じ……忘れてたかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe this isn’t so bad.\nThis feeling of having fun with everyone… I might have forgotten it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
